        <h2>Useful answers without unnecessary complexity</h2>

        <p>
            Sunset Guardian is an independent collection of financial 
            calculators built for people who want an answer without 
            creating an account. Calculator entries stay in the browser,
            and each tool explains the assumptions behind its results. 
            Supporting guides show how related calculations fit together
            and where simplified estimates may fall short.
        </p>

        <p>
            The goal is to reduce confusion and repetitive work while
            keeping the tools fast, private, and easy to use.
        </p>
